const Colors = {
	primary: "#fc5c65",
	secondary: "#4ecdc4",
	Img: require("../../assets/bg.png"),
	black: "#000",
	white: "#fff",
	grey: "#908e8c",
	medium: "#6e6969",
	light: "#f8f4f4",
	dark: "#0c0c0c",
	danger: "#ff5252",
	rgba: "rgba(255, 129, 126, 0.5)",
	profile: "rgba(130, 255, 163,1)"
};
export default Colors;
